2. The category2 ,category 3 

3. unsubscribe link style issue

4. filed value issue

6. missing utm for Explore L2 category, and browse button on footer

7. display price as $0 when price is Contactar, [https://www.vivanuncios.com.mx.staging2.qa-bolt.com/a-venta-inmuebles/tlaquepaque/dsaoij-dsaoidj-aosjd-osaijd-oasj-d/1001107571030910000180009?utm_source=alert&utm_source=system&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=bolt%3Futm_medium%3Demail&utm_campaign=automated-recommendations&utm_content=recommendation-number1]

9. New requirement for odd card:
 # Let's make the entire tile clickable
 # Let's make the tile links to L2 category [Inmuebles en venta] in this case. Same link with the orange button "Explora Inmuebles en venta" 
 # Let's give this card's utm content=view-all-card, and the orange button is view-all-button as 34857.

 

10. change to 1 resultado

11. change signature utm to utm_content=footer-homepage
